{"word":"συνδυάζω","slug":"συνδυάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνδυάζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>άσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to join two and two, couple</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>: —<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be coupled with something else</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be coupled, to pair</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}